spx.packets.tracks

Interface ThreatType


  • public interface ThreatType
    Values for the type field in the Threat structure that is contained within extended track reports.

    These constants are kept in sync with the SPX_PACKET_TRACK_THREAT_TYPE_... constants in "SPxPackets.h".

    See Also:
    Threat, Extended
